STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Vernon J. PARKER, Defendant-Petitioner. C-546 Sept. Term 2017
079891 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 2, 2018 **138To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-3133-13 and A-373-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

**139It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
